### Health Check
GET https://localhost:7019/health

### Ingest Documents - Valid Request
POST https://localhost:7019/api/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your-secret-api-key-here

{
  "documents": [
    {
      "id": "doc1",
      "title": "Sample Document 1",
      "content": "This is the content of the first document",
      "author": "John Doe",
      "category": "Technology",
      "tags": ["sample", "document", "test"]
    },
    {
      "id": "doc2", 
      "title": "Sample Document 2",
      "content": "This is the content of the second document",
      "author": "Jane Smith",
      "category": "Business",
      "tags": ["sample", "document", "business"]
    }
  ]
}

### Ingest Documents - Invalid API Key
POST https://localhost:7019/api/ingest
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: invalid-key

{
  "documents": [
    {
      "id": "doc1",
      "title": "Sample Document",
      "content": "This should fail due to invalid API key"
    }
  ]
}

